基于Linux pwm-beeper驱动

This is a fork of [pwm-beeper-test](https://github.com/Dangku/pwm-beeper-test) from (Dangku)[https://github.com/Dangku]. The source files has been modified so it can be built under the buildroot environnement.

Compile

$ git clone https://github.com/Dangku/pwm-beeper-test
$ cd pwm-beeper-test
$ cmake .
$ make

Test

$ ./pwm_auto /dev/input/eventX     //pwm-beeper create a input device
